2 General statistics of the score types

2.1 Reported interactions per score

interactions_long <- gather(interactions, key = score_name, value = score, 
                            -c(node1, node2, node1_string_id, node2_string_id))

occurences <- filter(interactions_long, score != 0, score_name != "combined_score") %>%
  group_by(score_name) %>% 
  summarize(n = n()) %>%
  mutate(percent = n / nrow(interactions)) %>%
  arrange(desc(percent))

ggplot(occurences, aes(x = reorder(score_name, percent), y = percent)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  coord_flip() +
  xlab("") +
  theme_bw()

2.2 Distributions of the score types

Histogram of the score types

ggplot(filter(interactions_long, score != 0), aes(x = score)) + 
  geom_histogram() + 
  facet_wrap(~score_name, scales = "free_y")
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

Stacked histogram

ggplot(filter(interactions_long, score != 0, score_name != "combined_score"), aes(x = score, fill = score_name)) + 
  geom_histogram() 
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

Percentages of each score type per bin

ggplot(filter(interactions_long, score != 0, score_name != "combined_score"), aes(x = score, fill = score_name)) + 
  geom_histogram(position = 'fill')
